title: Anthony Davis, Lakers-Pelicans, and free agency
itunes:title: Anthony Davis, Lakers-Pelicans, and free agency
description:
Colin discusses the Los Angeles Lakers getting F Anthony Davis from the New Orleans Pelicans and who won the trade. He also talks free agency and what the Lakers should do going forward. Guests include Chris Broussard, Bill Oram, and Doug Gottlieb.
